645
01:08:32,690 --> 01:08:36,182
哦，希望你没受太多苦，伍德
{\fscx70\fscy70}Oh, I sure hope you're not
in frightful pain, Wood.{\r}

646
01:08:36,761 --> 01:08:40,492
