{\fscx70\fscy70}A cat. It was on the roof
and I went after him.{\r}

688
01:13:04,527 --> 01:13:09,055
是只公猫，在嗷嗷叫，我就摔了
{\fscx70\fscy70}It was a tomcat yowling
and what all, and I slipped.{\r}

689
01:13:21,010 --> 01:13:24,104
我以为你畸形腿了呢
{\fscx70\fscy70}I thought maybe your club foot
was gaining on you.{\r}

690
01:13:33,156 --> 01:13:34,783
是啊
{\fscx70\fscy70}Oh, yeah.{\r}

691
01:13:35,558 --> 01:13:39,790
迪克去堪萨斯见他老婆去了
他之前在这呆过一阵子
{\fscx70\fscy70}Dick went to Kansas City to be
with his wife. He was here for a bit.{\r}

692
01:13:59,415 --> 01:14:02,316
对了杰西，给你讲个可爱的故事吧
{\fscx70\fscy70}Hey, here's a cute story, Jess.{\r}

693
01:14:02,485 --> 01:14:05,852
鲍勃11还是12岁的时候
{\fscx70\fscy70}Bobby was what, 11 or 12...{\r}

694
01:14:06,022 --> 01:14:09,185
非常非常仰慕你
{\fscx70\fscy70}...and you were by far
his most admired personage.{\r}

695
01:14:09,692 --> 01:14:10,852
不停地讲你
{\fscx70\fscy70}He couldn't get enough.{\r}

696
01:14:11,027 --> 01:14:15,225
“杰西这样”、“杰西那样”
一天到晚说不倦
{\fscx70\fscy70}It was "Jesse this" and "Jesse that"
and "Jesse this" from sunrise to sunset.{\r}

697
01:14:15,398 --> 01:14:16,524
真有趣
{\fscx70\fscy70}Fascinating.{\r}

698
01:14:16,699 --> 01:14:18,428
还有更逗的呢
{\fscx70\fscy70}No, there's more. This is cute.{\r}

699
