{\fscx70\fscy70}That'd be a good joke if it was funny.{\r}

710
01:15:02,812 --> 01:15:05,337
很逗吧，杰西？
{\fscx70\fscy70}Isn't that a cute story, Jess?{\r}

711
01:15:15,224 --> 01:15:18,091
多给我讲讲吧，鲍勃
{\fscx70\fscy70}Give me some more conversations, Bob.{\r}

712
01:15:23,166 --> 01:15:28,331
我想到了一个更牛的，是关于你…
{\fscx70\fscy70}I got one. This one's about as crackerjack...
