713
01:15:28,504 --> 01:15:30,404
让鲍勃讲吧
{\fscx70\fscy70}Let Bob tell it.{\r}

714
01:15:31,774 --> 01:15:33,571
好吧
{\fscx70\fscy70}All right.{\r}

715
01:15:40,116 --> 01:15:42,107
我都不知道你说什么
{\fscx70\fscy70}I don't even know
what you're talking about.{\r}

716
01:15:42,285 --> 01:15:46,278
你不是说你和杰西有很多共同点嘛
{\fscx70\fscy70}About how you and Jesse
