you and I overlap and whatnot.{\r}

724
01:16:27,463 --> 01:16:30,227
从我们的爸爸说起吧
{\fscx70\fscy70}I mean, you begin with our daddies.{\r}

725
01:16:30,399 --> 01:16:33,368
你爸爸是个浸信会牧师
{\fscx70\fscy70}Your daddy was a pastor
at the New Hope Baptist Church...{\r}

726
01:16:33,536 --> 01:16:38,269
而我爸爸是艾克塞尔西奥泉市的牧师
{\fscx70\fscy70}...and my daddy was a pastor
at the church in Excelsior Springs.{\r}

727
01:16:39,709 --> 01:16:44,043
你是家里三个兄弟中最小的
